WEBVTT

00:11.886 --> 00:12.929
You must be cold.

00:56.139 --> 01:00.727
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, your one-month free trial
of Boyfriend on Demand has ended.

01:01.478 --> 01:02.437
No.

01:03.229 --> 01:04.481
No!

01:06.441 --> 01:07.734
Don't go.

01:08.234 --> 01:09.569
No. You can't!

01:12.238 --> 01:13.573
Eun-ho…

01:14.240 --> 01:16.326
Don't let it end like this!

01:16.409 --> 01:17.827
No!

01:17.911 --> 01:19.412
SERVICE PERIOD EXPIRED

01:20.622 --> 01:21.831
Eun-ho!

01:26.836 --> 01:28.129
TRIAL ENDED

01:37.889 --> 01:39.015
Eun-ho…

01:42.852 --> 01:44.521
Evil bastards.

01:50.443 --> 01:55.949
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, please give a star rating
for your second date, Seo Eun-ho.

01:59.828 --> 02:03.832
HOW WAS YOUR DATE WITH SEO EUN-HO
IN &lt;SPRING, AND YOU&gt;?

02:03.915 --> 02:05.542
THANK YOU FOR PARTICIPATING

02:10.839 --> 02:11.756
No!

02:11.840 --> 02:13.424
EPISODE 4
NO RISK, HIGH RETURN

02:13.925 --> 02:15.635
ONE MONTH LATER

02:16.427 --> 02:20.849
The short-lived dream came to an end,
and I returned to my life.

02:21.724 --> 02:24.727
Awesome. TMTK and PlanC
are crushing it right now.

02:25.311 --> 02:29.816
Just as Yun Song said, her readers indeed
loved to hate-read out of habit,

02:29.899 --> 02:32.694
and The Man to Know did not fall easily.

02:33.236 --> 02:35.238
A long-running webtoon like TMTK is…

02:35.321 --> 02:38.199
But, of course,
I must never let my guard down.

02:38.283 --> 02:41.452
The next agenda is… Yes, the contest.

02:41.536 --> 02:43.163
It's that season again.

02:43.246 --> 02:46.457
This time, I didn't assign the genres
based on teams.

02:46.541 --> 02:48.960
I've personally allocated each of you.

02:49.586 --> 02:53.756
So, first up, fantasy.

02:54.340 --> 02:56.759
Choi Dong-min. Kim Seon-jeong.
You two are on it.

02:57.385 --> 02:58.219
-Okay.
-Okay.

02:58.303 --> 03:00.346
As for romantasy,

03:01.264 --> 03:03.516
Seo Mi-rae and

03:04.434 --> 03:06.311
Park Kyeong-nam. Congrats.

03:07.937 --> 03:10.523
Next, we have action.

03:12.233 --> 03:13.693
I let my guard down.

03:15.904 --> 03:17.614
Why was it you and not me?

03:17.697 --> 03:20.283
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

03:20.992 --> 03:22.493
I don't know either.

03:22.577 --> 03:23.912
Does he hate you or something?

03:24.495 --> 03:26.831
He's put you with Yun Song
and the nastiest genre.

03:26.915 --> 03:29.334
I'm asking why I wasn't picked.

03:29.417 --> 03:31.127
It's the most important genre.

03:31.211 --> 03:34.589
He handed it to those in charge of
the hottest webtoons right now.

03:34.672 --> 03:35.590
It's only natural.

03:35.673 --> 03:37.342
Just have some of this.

03:38.092 --> 03:40.845
Good on you for snagging us seats
far from the director.

03:40.929 --> 03:43.139
I had to camp out to get this table.

03:44.891 --> 03:45.808
Here.

03:46.809 --> 03:48.978
Hey, why have you been so down lately?

03:49.896 --> 03:50.730
Me?

03:52.273 --> 03:53.858
-Have I?
-Yeah.

03:54.359 --> 03:55.860
I noticed that too.

03:55.944 --> 03:58.446
Even at lunchtime, you seemed kind of

03:58.529 --> 04:00.198
wistful, I guess?

04:01.324 --> 04:04.953
Maybe she's just lonely.
It's almost the end of the year.

04:05.453 --> 04:06.537
Already?

04:07.205 --> 04:11.042
I've got a friend who's totally awesome.
Want me to set you up?

04:11.751 --> 04:14.879
If you start meeting up now,
you'll be dating by Christmas for sure.

04:14.963 --> 04:16.506
Yeah, set her up.

04:17.090 --> 04:18.841
-A blind date?
-He's younger than you.

04:18.925 --> 04:20.093
I have a picture of him.

04:21.511 --> 04:22.679
I'm good.

04:22.762 --> 04:25.431
Why not? You should accept these things
when you can.

04:25.515 --> 04:27.308
Well, I think I'm good.

04:27.392 --> 04:29.102
-Here it is!
-Let me see.

04:30.228 --> 04:32.146
Isn't he a catch?

04:32.230 --> 04:35.692
-Hey, he's so fine!
-Right?

04:35.775 --> 04:36.609
But

04:37.527 --> 04:39.362
you're already seeing someone.

04:40.613 --> 04:41.656
Who is?

04:43.366 --> 04:44.284
Ms. Seo.

04:45.118 --> 04:46.160
-Huh?
-What?

04:47.203 --> 04:49.080
-Nah!
-Nah!

04:50.081 --> 04:52.417
Wait, what are you talking about?

04:52.500 --> 04:57.130
You told me you had a date last time,
so I thought you had a boyfriend.

04:59.048 --> 05:03.052
Please, that was ages ago.
It was just a date, nothing serious.

05:04.554 --> 05:07.974
I mean, I got introduced to a guy
a while back.

05:08.057 --> 05:09.392
It was really brief.

05:10.059 --> 05:12.895
I see. I must have misunderstood.

05:13.896 --> 05:15.481
Ms. Seo, you wound me.

05:15.565 --> 05:16.983
-Huh?
-Me too.

05:17.066 --> 05:20.486
I knew you had clear boundaries,
but this one quite stings.

05:21.237 --> 05:25.033
No, I never mentioned it
because it really was nothing.

05:25.116 --> 05:28.036
She doesn't have to tell us
every little detail about her dates.

05:28.119 --> 05:29.203
Still…

05:30.371 --> 05:33.875
Anyway, does that mean
you're not seeing anyone right now?

05:34.375 --> 05:35.209
I'm not.

05:35.293 --> 05:37.170
How about that blind date? Go, go?

05:37.253 --> 05:38.671
-Go, go.
-Go, go.

05:41.966 --> 05:42.884
No, I'm good.

05:42.967 --> 05:44.302
That's it. Don't set her up.

05:44.385 --> 05:47.180
I get it.
She might not be into younger guys.

05:48.181 --> 05:50.224
Younger guys are my thing, you know.

05:50.725 --> 05:51.976
Would you like to take it?

05:53.019 --> 05:56.105
Well, you can show me that picture again.

05:56.189 --> 05:57.065
Sure.

05:58.316 --> 05:59.484
Where does he live?

05:59.567 --> 06:00.651
He lives in Seoul.

06:00.735 --> 06:02.570
I knew it. I live in Seoul too.

06:02.653 --> 06:04.030
-Isn't it great?
-It is.

06:04.113 --> 06:06.824
I've always preferred Seoul guys.
They live nearby and all.

06:07.700 --> 06:09.452
Why, that little…

06:12.497 --> 06:14.165
Man, aren't you cold?

06:14.248 --> 06:15.666
Hey, let's go!

06:15.750 --> 06:18.002
Thank you for the meal!

06:18.086 --> 06:19.337
See you all tomorrow!

06:21.172 --> 06:22.090
I've got to run.

06:22.173 --> 06:24.133
Hey, I'm buying. How about round two?

06:24.217 --> 06:25.426
-Round two, it is.
-Where…

06:25.510 --> 06:27.011
-Where are you going?
-Good night.

06:27.095 --> 06:27.929
Guys?

06:28.012 --> 06:29.764
-I'll be going, then.
-All right.

06:29.847 --> 06:31.099
Have a good night!

06:36.396 --> 06:37.730
-Where are you headed?
-What?

06:38.231 --> 06:40.149
Oh, I'm struggling to get a cab.

06:40.650 --> 06:43.152
Same. I'm sure we'll catch one on the way.

06:45.571 --> 06:46.406
Did

06:47.156 --> 06:49.492
what I said earlier bother you?

06:50.451 --> 06:51.577
Sorry?

06:51.661 --> 06:55.498
You know, how I brought up
your private life in front of everyone.

06:57.667 --> 06:59.669
It's fine. It was just a misunderstanding.

07:00.503 --> 07:03.005
Sorry about that.
I'm a bit slow on the uptake.

07:03.089 --> 07:04.841
You just realized that?

07:06.008 --> 07:07.176
I see.

07:10.221 --> 07:12.723
I look forward to
judging the submissions with you.

07:13.349 --> 07:15.768
Did you know we would be teamed up?

07:15.852 --> 07:16.853
No, I didn't.

07:18.771 --> 07:22.442
If you want to change partners,
we can talk to the director together.

07:23.192 --> 07:25.194
-You hate it that much?
-Huh?

07:25.278 --> 07:26.696
Having to judge with me.

07:28.990 --> 07:30.491
No, it's not like that.

07:31.075 --> 07:33.578
Then… let's do it together.

07:37.874 --> 07:39.333
I see taxis.

07:43.129 --> 07:44.922
Take the first one.

07:46.632 --> 07:47.758
Are you sure?

07:48.718 --> 07:49.552
What do you mean?

07:51.721 --> 07:52.555
Go ahead.

07:53.973 --> 07:56.142
Okay, then. Have a nice weekend.

07:56.225 --> 07:57.977
Right. You too.

07:58.060 --> 07:59.270
Cold!

08:03.608 --> 08:04.984
Hi. Yongsan, please.

08:05.485 --> 08:06.569
I don't go there.

08:07.069 --> 08:08.070
What?

08:08.154 --> 08:11.073
This is an Incheon taxi.
You should've looked before getting in.

08:12.867 --> 08:14.076
Sorry.

08:18.080 --> 08:19.457
INCHEON

08:20.958 --> 08:22.877
Are you kidding me?

08:23.544 --> 08:24.795
You could've told me!

08:39.977 --> 08:43.272
"I look forward to working with you"?
Could've fooled me.

08:51.447 --> 08:53.699
1: THE MAN TO KNOW
2: PlanC

08:53.783 --> 08:55.785
Always on our tail.
It's making me nervous.

08:58.621 --> 09:00.581
Here to cleanse my eyes
of the rotten TMTK.

09:00.665 --> 09:02.333
TMTK beat this? The system's rigged.

09:02.416 --> 09:04.585
Hwany is a god. PlanC is god-tier!

09:04.669 --> 09:06.504
JI-YEON

09:07.004 --> 09:09.257
Hey. What's up? It's late.

09:09.340 --> 09:11.842
Why haven't you been replying
in the group chat?

09:13.052 --> 09:14.512
I must've missed it. What is it?

09:14.595 --> 09:16.430
-You know it's tomorrow, right?
-Huh?

09:17.181 --> 09:19.016
An Da-yeong's housewarming party.

09:21.811 --> 09:22.937
Right.

09:23.437 --> 09:24.981
I knew this would happen.

09:25.064 --> 09:26.232
Don't forget.

09:28.359 --> 09:29.402
See you tomorrow.

09:34.574 --> 09:36.075
What should I buy?

09:40.121 --> 09:41.414
-Over there.
-Look at this.

09:41.497 --> 09:43.332
Oh my God!

09:44.333 --> 09:46.043
-Enjoy your time.
-Thank you.

09:46.127 --> 09:47.545
-Thank you.
-Excuse me.

09:47.628 --> 09:49.255
Is an idol coming here?

09:49.755 --> 09:53.134
No, this is the line
for the Boyfriend on Demand pop-up store.

09:54.594 --> 09:56.429
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND
ENTRY NUMBER 454

10:01.642 --> 10:03.394
Right this way!

10:08.482 --> 10:10.943
-Let me show you.
-Would you like to try it on?

10:19.910 --> 10:21.120
Ms. Seo?

10:22.538 --> 10:23.789
-Hello.
-Hi there.

10:24.373 --> 10:25.625
How nice of you to come.

10:25.708 --> 10:27.793
I could have reserved you a spot.

10:27.877 --> 10:30.588
No, I just happened to be passing by.

10:30.671 --> 10:31.505
Is that so?

10:32.131 --> 10:35.509
Yes. This is quite a turnout.

10:35.593 --> 10:37.053
Yes. Isn't it amazing?

10:37.845 --> 10:41.265
We should have the highest sales
of any pop-up here this year.

10:43.059 --> 10:44.518
Congratulations, Mr. Min.

10:45.019 --> 10:47.313
All thanks to your hard work
reviewing our product.

10:47.396 --> 10:48.481
Are you enjoying it?

10:50.107 --> 10:51.942
-Enjoying what?
-Boyfriend on Demand.

10:56.280 --> 10:57.198
Well…

10:58.449 --> 11:01.952
I actually haven't been playing.
I stopped playing back then.

11:02.828 --> 11:04.080
Is that right?

11:04.163 --> 11:08.417
You sounded very satisfied in your review.
We even gave you the device.

11:08.501 --> 11:11.504
I was sure you'd subscribe
once it hit the market.

11:12.672 --> 11:15.299
I appreciate the gift,
but I've just been busy with life.

11:16.050 --> 11:20.054
Still, doesn't Boyfriend on Demand
blow real life out of the water?

11:23.349 --> 11:26.102
I'm not sure.
I'd say real life is still better.

11:27.645 --> 11:28.813
How heartless of you.

11:28.896 --> 11:32.650
You can take a look while you're here.
I'll show you around.

11:32.733 --> 11:33.651
Oh, I can't.

11:33.734 --> 11:36.487
I'm here for some last-minute shopping,
so I should go.

11:37.947 --> 11:40.282
I'll see you around, then.

11:40.366 --> 11:41.951
-Thank you.
-Good luck!

11:46.580 --> 11:47.832
That was unexpected.

11:55.423 --> 11:56.257
Hey, what's up?

11:56.340 --> 11:58.050
You didn't forget, did you?

11:58.551 --> 12:02.096
Of course not. I'm not a goldfish.
I'm out buying a gift right now.

12:02.179 --> 12:03.681
That's good to hear.

12:04.598 --> 12:06.475
I need to tell you something.

12:06.559 --> 12:09.145
-You do?
-Promise me you won't get mad.

12:09.228 --> 12:10.354
What is it?

12:10.438 --> 12:13.607
Someone else will be joining us
at Da-yeong's place today.

12:13.691 --> 12:14.525
Who?

12:15.484 --> 12:17.778
Just some guy Da-yeong knows.

12:18.821 --> 12:19.905
We're setting you up.

12:22.700 --> 12:23.576
Hello?

12:24.702 --> 12:26.454
Come on, say something!

12:29.373 --> 12:31.834
We didn't tell you, and that's on us.

12:31.917 --> 12:34.879
We were gonna keep it secret
and pretend it was all organic,

12:35.463 --> 12:40.009
but then we got super worried
that you might show up in sweats.

12:41.051 --> 12:42.219
Hello?

12:42.970 --> 12:45.264
Did I screw up again? Are you mad?

12:48.017 --> 12:48.851
No.

12:49.602 --> 12:50.436
Huh?

12:50.936 --> 12:51.937
Well done.

12:52.021 --> 12:53.189
Well done?

12:53.272 --> 12:55.357
Yeah. See you later.

12:55.441 --> 12:56.567
Okay.

12:59.820 --> 13:00.654
What's with her?

13:15.711 --> 13:17.379
-Is she running late?
-Don't know!

13:17.463 --> 13:18.631
Seriously?

13:21.258 --> 13:23.302
She's always late.
She should be here soon.

13:23.886 --> 13:24.845
Okay.

13:29.725 --> 13:30.810
Hey, what…

13:32.144 --> 13:33.479
Mi-rae, you're here…

13:44.406 --> 13:45.574
Sorry I'm late.

13:45.658 --> 13:47.243
Hey, that outfit…

13:47.326 --> 13:49.703
Hey, this one looks decent.

13:52.206 --> 13:53.666
Am I wearing this a bit late?

13:54.458 --> 13:56.377
No. It's meant to be a winter outfit.

13:56.460 --> 13:57.670
Come in.

14:01.173 --> 14:03.717
-Shall we have a drink?
-All right.

14:03.801 --> 14:05.052
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

14:09.056 --> 14:10.057
Thanks for coming.

14:10.140 --> 14:11.976
-Totally.
-Of course we came.

14:12.059 --> 14:14.353
-Have some of this.
-Thank you.

14:15.521 --> 14:16.564
Is it good?

14:16.647 --> 14:18.107
-Delicious. So good.
-It's good.

14:19.942 --> 14:20.943
Here.

14:21.443 --> 14:22.570
Thank you.

14:24.488 --> 14:26.490
-A guy with manners.
-Your glass is empty.

14:27.157 --> 14:28.409
Thank you.

14:31.412 --> 14:33.038
-Cheers, everyone?
-Sure.

14:33.956 --> 14:34.874
Cheers!

14:34.957 --> 14:37.418
APT!

14:37.501 --> 14:38.335
Seventh floor!

14:38.419 --> 14:40.880
One. Two. Three. Four. Five. Six. Seven!

14:42.089 --> 14:43.924
Down the hatch it goes!

14:44.008 --> 14:44.842
Bunny!

14:44.925 --> 14:45.926
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

14:46.010 --> 14:46.844
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

14:46.927 --> 14:47.887
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

14:47.970 --> 14:48.971
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

14:49.054 --> 14:50.097
Carrot…

14:51.473 --> 14:52.474
I'll drink that.

14:53.058 --> 14:54.393
So sweet!

14:59.148 --> 15:00.316
Seo Mi-rae won again.

15:00.399 --> 15:01.650
You two are so good.

15:01.734 --> 15:03.152
I want my boyfriend here now.

15:03.235 --> 15:04.612
Hey, you don't mean…

15:05.112 --> 15:06.447
Hey!

15:06.530 --> 15:09.033
-Are you okay? Where are the napkins?
-Are you okay?

15:09.909 --> 15:11.827
Good thing you didn't get drenched.

15:11.911 --> 15:13.120
Thank you.

15:13.203 --> 15:14.163
This is going well.

15:17.458 --> 15:18.959
Happy, Mi-rae?

15:20.920 --> 15:21.921
Cheers.

15:22.004 --> 15:23.422
Let's drink, guys.

15:23.505 --> 15:24.924
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

15:26.258 --> 15:27.760
I had a great time today.

15:29.929 --> 15:32.932
I'm quite an introvert,
but you made me feel comfortable,

15:33.015 --> 15:34.767
so I enjoyed it a lot too.

15:34.850 --> 15:37.186
Really? That's nice to hear.

15:38.395 --> 15:41.273
Da-yeong said
a lot of great things about you.

15:41.941 --> 15:45.486
Now that I've met you,
you do seem like a really nice person.

15:45.569 --> 15:46.612
And you're cute.

15:49.031 --> 15:50.366
What did you think?

15:50.991 --> 15:51.825
Sorry?

15:52.326 --> 15:53.202
Of me.

15:55.913 --> 15:57.790
I also had a good time.

15:58.415 --> 16:01.210
That's good. Does that mean
we can see each other again?

16:01.710 --> 16:03.087
Yes, I guess so.

16:03.796 --> 16:06.173
You live near Yongsan,

16:06.256 --> 16:08.926
so that's about two hours away
from my place.

16:10.219 --> 16:12.221
You're busy on weekdays, aren't you?

16:12.304 --> 16:13.555
I'm afraid so.

16:15.015 --> 16:17.059
Would you like to meet up next weekend?

16:17.142 --> 16:18.143
Lunch on Saturday?

16:18.227 --> 16:20.270
I can also do dinner on Friday.

16:21.355 --> 16:22.856
I'll check my schedule.

16:24.441 --> 16:27.027
Can you check now?
I'd really like to set up a date.

16:27.611 --> 16:30.030
I'll check later once I get home.

16:32.241 --> 16:33.158
Mi-rae.

16:36.954 --> 16:38.455
Do you not like me?

16:39.039 --> 16:39.873
What?

16:40.833 --> 16:44.253
Please be honest with me now
instead of turning me down tomorrow.

16:45.546 --> 16:48.841
It's nothing like that.
We only just met today and--

16:48.924 --> 16:52.219
Come on, we're not children.

16:53.345 --> 16:55.180
You can just be honest with me.

16:56.432 --> 16:57.349
Excuse me.

16:57.850 --> 17:00.686
What exactly are you telling me
to be honest about?

17:02.479 --> 17:03.731
Did I upset you?

17:04.648 --> 17:08.777
Lately, I've met a lot of people
who were just testing the waters.

17:08.861 --> 17:11.405
I must've been on edge. I'm sorry.

17:11.488 --> 17:14.616
I know you're not one to test the waters…

17:14.700 --> 17:17.619
You keep saying "testing the waters,"

17:18.162 --> 17:20.956
but everyone has their own pace, you know.

17:22.791 --> 17:23.625
Right.

17:31.300 --> 17:35.137
I had fun today, and I'm sorry,
but I can go alone from here.

17:35.220 --> 17:36.638
But it's so late--

17:36.722 --> 17:37.890
I'll be fine.

17:38.390 --> 17:40.434
Get home safe, Min-gyu.

17:50.069 --> 17:53.864
What that guy said may have been right.

17:54.698 --> 17:56.450
My pace wasn't the issue.

17:57.618 --> 17:59.912
I just wasn't ready
to go out with someone.

18:01.121 --> 18:03.624
But I just had to jump into a blind date.

18:07.419 --> 18:08.796
I must have been crazy.

18:10.255 --> 18:11.799
What was I thinking?

18:16.678 --> 18:17.638
Excuse me.

18:19.640 --> 18:20.557
Got you.

18:22.434 --> 18:24.561
REQUESTING A DRIVER WITHIN 8 MINUTES

18:24.645 --> 18:26.480
NO AVAILABLE TAXIS NEARBY

18:31.777 --> 18:33.612
I'm sorry.

18:38.575 --> 18:39.868
What the heck?

19:32.504 --> 19:33.714
No way.

19:35.132 --> 19:36.175
Mi-rae.

19:37.426 --> 19:38.260
Eun-ho.

19:38.969 --> 19:40.095
Seo Eun-ho!

19:42.764 --> 19:45.392
Eun-ho!

19:48.187 --> 19:49.021
Eun-ho!

19:51.356 --> 19:52.649
Eun-ho!

20:06.622 --> 20:07.623
Eun-ho!

20:11.001 --> 20:12.836
It's been so long since we last met.

20:16.882 --> 20:18.050
How have you been?

20:30.145 --> 20:33.482
Would you be my girlfriend?
See you in Boyfriend on Demand.

20:44.993 --> 20:47.162
"Basic."

20:47.246 --> 20:49.414
"500,000 won a month."

20:50.415 --> 20:51.250
500,000?

20:51.333 --> 20:52.251
500,000?!

20:52.751 --> 20:54.419
You're out of your damn mind!

20:56.546 --> 20:58.465
How dare you exploit loneliness
for profit!

20:58.548 --> 21:00.842
What a bunch of scumbags!

21:01.718 --> 21:02.970
Forget it. Not buying.

21:08.892 --> 21:09.726
Hang on.

21:09.810 --> 21:12.938
When dating in real life, did you spend
less than 500,000 won a month?

21:13.021 --> 21:14.189
No.

21:15.023 --> 21:18.026
Dinners, gifts,
occasional trips, and clothes…

21:18.110 --> 21:20.279
I'd spend well over 500,000 won.

21:21.363 --> 21:22.197
No.

21:22.281 --> 21:25.367
Could you ever meet someone
better than Seo Eun-ho in real life?

21:26.118 --> 21:26.952
No.

21:27.035 --> 21:30.455
Does Boyfriend on Demand involve any risks
beyond the monthly fee?

21:30.539 --> 21:31.415
No.

21:31.498 --> 21:34.084
Is Boyfriend on Demand
a hindrance to my career?

21:34.167 --> 21:35.002
No.

21:35.085 --> 21:37.504
Does Boyfriend on Demand make me happier?

21:39.631 --> 21:43.552
Then is there a reason for me
not to use Boyfriend on Demand?

21:46.430 --> 21:47.264
PAYMENT COMPLETE

21:51.810 --> 21:53.770
Personalization process complete.

22:00.068 --> 22:03.655
Place the ring on your head
and assume a comfortable position.

22:03.739 --> 22:05.365
When you press the button,

22:05.449 --> 22:07.784
the ring will light up
and begin connecting.

22:31.224 --> 22:32.267
Am I in a hotel?

22:40.525 --> 22:41.360
Who…

22:42.527 --> 22:43.528
You scared me!

22:43.612 --> 22:45.989
You're here? Long time no see.

22:48.158 --> 22:49.034
So you remember me.

22:49.826 --> 22:50.827
You weren't reset?

22:50.911 --> 22:52.371
Do you take me for an idiot?

22:54.456 --> 22:57.542
Where are we anyway?
Where are all the posters?

23:00.837 --> 23:02.130
This is your house.

23:02.214 --> 23:03.256
What?

23:03.340 --> 23:04.716
Your house.

23:04.800 --> 23:07.594
You'll be living here from now on
in Boyfriend on Demand.

23:08.762 --> 23:12.516
It's a gift for your regular subscription.
Take your time and look around.

23:14.142 --> 23:15.060
Oh my God!

23:58.395 --> 23:59.229
That dress…

23:59.312 --> 24:00.647
Did Choi Si-woo get you that?

24:02.023 --> 24:02.858
Yes.

24:03.608 --> 24:05.068
How did it end up here?

24:05.569 --> 24:08.738
The gifts you received will remain,
and as for the rest,

24:09.239 --> 24:11.992
they get updated with brand-new items
once every month.

24:17.038 --> 24:18.373
Why are you so nice to me?

24:18.874 --> 24:21.209
That's what our subscribers deserve.

24:22.210 --> 24:27.257
You must go through a lot in real life.
I want you to be nothing but happy here.

24:30.343 --> 24:32.304
Let me just calm down for a bit.

24:38.518 --> 24:41.396
Let me know when you're done.
I'll show you the view.

24:42.772 --> 24:43.899
The view?

25:13.595 --> 25:17.349
Now you can date your boyfriend
in this house.

25:18.433 --> 25:19.267
In here?

25:19.351 --> 25:21.436
Why else would the house be so big?

25:28.068 --> 25:28.985
OPERATION 0125

25:29.069 --> 25:31.988
HEART-POUNDING ACTION ROMANCE
LOVE IN THE SKY

25:32.572 --> 25:35.158
You've seen everything.
It's time for you to go on a date.

25:36.701 --> 25:38.662
Wait. I have something to say.

25:38.745 --> 25:40.038
What is it?

25:41.289 --> 25:44.042
It's about me and Seo Eun-ho.

25:48.505 --> 25:50.173
Things ended abruptly,

25:50.257 --> 25:53.552
you know, at a really crucial moment.

25:56.263 --> 25:57.472
Which is why…

26:00.225 --> 26:02.477
I'd like to meet Seo Eun-ho again.

26:03.562 --> 26:06.565
Picking up from that scene.

26:09.442 --> 26:10.610
But you can't.

26:12.404 --> 26:13.989
What? Why not?

26:14.072 --> 26:16.700
If you want to go straight
for the guy you want,

26:16.783 --> 26:19.703
you need to get on the premium plan,
not the basic plan.

26:20.537 --> 26:21.538
Premium?

26:22.914 --> 26:25.917
"Basic. 500,000 won a month."

26:26.001 --> 26:27.460
"Premium."

26:27.961 --> 26:29.671
One million?

26:30.297 --> 26:33.216
Hello? That's ridiculous.
You're kidding, right?

26:33.300 --> 26:36.469
In the basic plan, you can only date
those I match you with.

26:37.053 --> 26:37.887
Then

26:38.888 --> 26:41.641
does that mean
I can't meet Seo Eun-ho right now?

26:41.725 --> 26:42.851
No.

26:47.814 --> 26:48.690
No way.

26:50.233 --> 26:53.403
What are you waiting for?
Go get your money's worth, girl.

26:53.486 --> 26:54.738
Don't play it safe.

26:55.488 --> 26:56.323
My money's worth?

26:56.906 --> 27:01.661
What's the issue when there are 898 men
besides Seo Eun-ho and Choi Si-woo?

27:03.830 --> 27:07.417
In here, you can bounce
between ten guys in a single day,

27:07.500 --> 27:09.502
and no one will judge you.

27:10.003 --> 27:12.839
Even if you got rejected ten times,
no one would mock you.

27:15.133 --> 27:18.386
So live it up a little, okay?

27:19.596 --> 27:20.680
She's right.

27:21.181 --> 27:24.392
Here, I'm not expected
to be loyal to a boyfriend.

27:24.476 --> 27:26.770
There are no talking stage rules,

27:27.270 --> 27:30.065
and no one laughs at me
for getting rejected.

27:34.653 --> 27:35.487
Enjoy your trip.

27:45.622 --> 27:46.456
What?

27:49.542 --> 27:50.377
What?

27:51.503 --> 27:53.088
Am I a flight attendant?

28:11.022 --> 28:12.107
That's heavy.

28:13.274 --> 28:14.609
That high?

28:15.860 --> 28:17.821
Why couldn't they make me taller?

28:24.452 --> 28:25.954
So it's a foreigner this time.

28:58.862 --> 28:59.821
Oh my.

29:11.916 --> 29:13.960
Just like that, without any warning?

29:14.919 --> 29:16.838
I'm working right now, so--

29:21.676 --> 29:22.761
It's a gun!

29:56.753 --> 29:58.588
What's a gun doing on a plane?

29:58.671 --> 29:59.839
What the heck?

30:05.678 --> 30:07.180
This is what I get for paying up?

30:12.977 --> 30:15.355
Damn it. I should get out of here.

30:18.775 --> 30:20.109
Oh God!

30:46.803 --> 30:47.929
You're okay now.

30:48.012 --> 30:50.557
That was an incident
involving a terrorist group.

30:55.520 --> 30:56.604
BAE HYEON-WOO
NIS

30:59.107 --> 31:03.069
Congratulations, Ms. Seo Mi-rae,
on meeting your third date!

31:04.404 --> 31:07.198
The production value
of the paid version is just…

31:07.282 --> 31:09.075
The NIS, really?

31:15.206 --> 31:18.084
Would you mind
calming the passengers down first?

31:18.167 --> 31:19.043
What?

31:24.507 --> 31:25.341
Right.

31:29.470 --> 31:31.472
-Thank you for bearing with us.
-Excuse me.

31:33.474 --> 31:35.393
-Are you okay?
-My head is a bit--

31:35.476 --> 31:37.312
-It's a gun!
-Gun!

31:39.939 --> 31:41.232
Hold on tight!

31:55.496 --> 31:57.832
Why are you doing this to me?

32:13.848 --> 32:14.974
Are you okay?

32:16.351 --> 32:17.185
What was that?

32:19.354 --> 32:22.982
I'm so scared right now.
I can't even go on the pirate ship ride.

32:23.066 --> 32:25.443
I don't think this one's right for me.

32:26.277 --> 32:28.029
Well, goodbye.

32:36.037 --> 32:36.955
Doctor!

32:37.038 --> 32:39.040
Come on!
The patient's vitals are dropping!

32:39.123 --> 32:39.958
What?

32:40.458 --> 32:42.460
INTERN SEO MI-RAE

32:45.588 --> 32:47.298
-Scalpel?
-What?

32:47.882 --> 32:48.800
Hey!

32:55.932 --> 32:57.517
Get a grip, will you?

32:58.977 --> 32:59.894
Move.

32:59.978 --> 33:01.312
Did you check his rhythm?

33:02.188 --> 33:03.523
Prepare to defibrillate. Gel.

33:06.109 --> 33:07.110
The gel!

33:13.950 --> 33:14.784
200 joules.

33:16.119 --> 33:16.995
200 joules!

33:19.038 --> 33:20.540
What? Is this a touch screen?

33:20.623 --> 33:22.125
On the side!

33:24.752 --> 33:25.837
Below!

33:27.088 --> 33:28.589
One, two, three, shock.

33:31.009 --> 33:32.927
-Can you hear me, sir?
-Yes.

33:34.846 --> 33:36.347
Thank you so much.

33:37.807 --> 33:38.725
Come with me.

33:46.274 --> 33:48.026
You nearly killed him. You know that?

33:49.444 --> 33:50.695
Answer me!

33:53.573 --> 33:56.659
Goodness. What a total hothead.

33:58.578 --> 33:59.746
Seo Mi-rae.

34:01.497 --> 34:02.331
Yes?

34:02.915 --> 34:04.167
Why won't you ever

34:05.293 --> 34:06.210
give me an answer?

34:08.963 --> 34:12.050
It's been over a week now.
Are you trying to leave me hanging?

34:14.302 --> 34:16.220
I'm not sure I follow…

34:18.765 --> 34:20.600
You're gonna pretend it didn't happen?

34:20.683 --> 34:21.934
I'd love that!

34:27.482 --> 34:29.067
Did you see that?

34:33.362 --> 34:34.822
If you don't remember,

34:36.199 --> 34:37.200
let me remind you.

34:39.660 --> 34:40.495
I…

34:42.580 --> 34:43.623
like you.

34:47.752 --> 34:49.629
A fiery senior's secret crush.

34:50.546 --> 34:51.714
It's a classic.

34:52.882 --> 34:53.883
Would you…

34:55.927 --> 34:57.303
give me a chance now?

35:00.056 --> 35:01.557
You're killing me.

35:12.527 --> 35:13.653
I think I get it now.

35:19.242 --> 35:22.036
Why Ji-yeon keeps
putting herself out there.

35:33.840 --> 35:37.135
The person I'd like to go
to Paradise with is

35:38.553 --> 35:40.096
Seo Mi-rae!

35:52.567 --> 35:53.568
Ms. Seo.

35:58.990 --> 36:00.908
Your argument leaned too much on emotion.

36:00.992 --> 36:04.871
The same could be said of you.
You tend to be too aloof.

36:04.954 --> 36:06.747
Court demands a cool head.

36:06.831 --> 36:07.874
But…

36:12.962 --> 36:14.589
no need to be aloof right now.

36:17.508 --> 36:18.718
Are you busy tonight?

36:23.431 --> 36:26.225
In here, love is above the law…

36:41.157 --> 36:42.116
What's this?

36:44.452 --> 36:45.369
"Diyu"?

36:51.375 --> 36:52.376
Stop.

36:53.544 --> 36:54.378
Who goes there?

36:55.129 --> 36:57.131
I'm a sworn enemy of this family.

37:01.010 --> 37:02.053
Hand that over,

37:02.553 --> 37:04.138
and I'll spare your life.

37:13.272 --> 37:14.357
Stop right there!

37:16.067 --> 37:17.318
If you come any closer…

37:44.845 --> 37:47.306
…and you can even fall in love
with a sworn enemy.

37:57.024 --> 37:58.776
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND
REVIEW SUBMISSION

37:59.402 --> 38:01.821
Unni, look over here!

38:40.151 --> 38:40.985
Are you okay?

38:42.820 --> 38:43.654
Yes.

38:50.202 --> 38:56.625
I literally gulped down the dates
that Boyfriend on Demand spoon-fed me.

38:57.710 --> 38:59.962
It was like I had been parched
all this time.

39:00.921 --> 39:04.342
But why bother meeting men
in a virtual reality, you ask?

39:10.514 --> 39:14.101
Well, there's no denying that there are
attractive men in the real world.

39:16.937 --> 39:18.439
But Boyfriend on Demand

39:19.690 --> 39:21.609
even lets me meet Jay Park.

39:39.251 --> 39:41.253
WOULD YOU ACCEPT A SECRET DATE
WITH JAY PARK?

39:46.300 --> 39:47.676
You look pretty today.

40:01.816 --> 40:03.984
SPECIAL DATE
A SECRET RELATIONSHIP WITH JAY PARK

40:04.693 --> 40:06.570
How can you not get a second date?

40:06.654 --> 40:09.031
I don't know. It's so annoying.

40:09.115 --> 40:11.617
I had a good feeling
since our date was on my birthday.

40:11.700 --> 40:12.952
And I really liked him.

40:14.203 --> 40:15.037
Show me the texts.

40:20.876 --> 40:23.129
Hey, Mi-rae. Check this out.

40:23.212 --> 40:26.006
This guy wrote, "Happy birthday, ma'am."

40:26.882 --> 40:28.384
How old does he think she is?

40:28.467 --> 40:32.096
He's just a really polite guy.

40:33.097 --> 40:36.100
-He probably won't stay in touch, right?
-No, ma'am.

40:36.809 --> 40:38.436
Try texting him first, like,

40:38.519 --> 40:41.021
"What are you up to?"
"When should we meet up?"

40:41.105 --> 40:42.523
That's absurd.

40:42.606 --> 40:43.774
Hurry up and do it.

40:43.858 --> 40:46.318
She'd never be able to do it herself.

40:46.402 --> 40:47.319
Totally.

40:48.696 --> 40:50.072
Here. I'll do it for you.

40:50.156 --> 40:51.407
What are you doing?

40:51.490 --> 40:52.783
For real? Wait!

40:53.367 --> 40:56.579
Have you really lost it?
Don't send it. Don't!

40:56.662 --> 40:57.746
She actually sent it.

41:02.710 --> 41:03.878
He read it!

41:04.378 --> 41:05.838
Oh no!

41:06.338 --> 41:07.965
Don't hang around in the chat.

41:08.048 --> 41:10.009
Reading messages right away isn't cool.

41:12.261 --> 41:14.972
You're talking like a dating pro
all of a sudden.

41:15.723 --> 41:17.516
Did you get a reply? What did he say?

41:18.058 --> 41:20.478
-No way.
-What the hell?

41:21.061 --> 41:23.147
-He asked her out for this weekend.
-See?

41:23.647 --> 41:26.066
Ask first. If it works, great.
If not, move on.

41:26.150 --> 41:29.069
That's Dating 101. Write it down.

41:32.406 --> 41:33.699
I should take this.

41:34.658 --> 41:35.534
Sure.

41:37.161 --> 41:38.245
Yes, Ms. Yun.

41:38.329 --> 41:40.039
What's gotten into her?

41:40.122 --> 41:41.707
Do you think she's possessed?

41:50.174 --> 41:51.300
Iced Americano, please.

41:51.383 --> 41:54.136
That will be 4,000 won.

41:54.887 --> 41:55.721
Thanks.

42:03.604 --> 42:05.356
I see you're buying just a cup today.

42:06.106 --> 42:06.941
Excuse me?

42:08.025 --> 42:11.445
Last time, you bought another one
to drink on your way home.

42:14.657 --> 42:16.492
Here's your iced latte.

42:19.245 --> 42:21.497
Buying two wasn't necessary today.

42:24.083 --> 42:26.877
Hwany must be late with his file today.
How unusual.

42:28.128 --> 42:30.506
It looks like he's going hard this week.

42:36.136 --> 42:37.137
Is that so?

42:37.638 --> 42:40.224
Still, I doubt we're going to beat TMTK.

42:41.475 --> 42:44.311
I guess it's another late submission
with Ms. Yun tonight.

42:48.148 --> 42:48.983
No.

42:49.066 --> 42:52.194
We are also going hard this week, you see.

42:53.737 --> 42:55.197
Oh, is that right?

42:56.490 --> 42:58.576
Here's your Americano.

43:12.256 --> 43:13.090
I need a straw.

43:33.527 --> 43:35.321
It's about time you sent it. Come on.

43:45.039 --> 43:46.040
I'm heading out first.

43:47.625 --> 43:48.876
Sure. Good night.

43:48.959 --> 43:50.669
Right. Good luck.

43:58.010 --> 43:59.345
What am I going to do?

43:59.803 --> 44:00.638
YUN SONG

44:07.227 --> 44:08.062
UPLOAD COMPLETE

44:12.066 --> 44:13.442
I'm home.

44:13.525 --> 44:15.194
Initiating home mode.

44:19.740 --> 44:21.241
God, I'm wiped out.

44:27.456 --> 44:28.457
Let's see now.

44:39.426 --> 44:41.720
-Is the spelling for real?
-It has to be a joke.

44:41.804 --> 44:43.138
The worst typo ever.

44:43.222 --> 44:44.973
Doesn't Naemo even have an editor?

44:45.057 --> 44:47.810
Choi Si-woo goes out in a blaze of idiocy.
God save him!

44:50.312 --> 44:53.107
"Sorry to brother you,
but I'll be taking this woman."

44:54.358 --> 44:55.192
"Brother"?

44:56.110 --> 44:57.486
What am I looking at?

44:57.569 --> 44:59.238
Are you kidding me?!

44:59.321 --> 45:01.323
BROTHER

45:11.208 --> 45:13.377
Excuse me, sir?

45:13.460 --> 45:14.461
I'm sorry.

45:15.587 --> 45:18.006
So he "brothers" to take her away,

45:18.090 --> 45:20.300
buys her a giant diamond ring,
and proposes?

45:23.887 --> 45:25.222
Have you

45:25.305 --> 45:26.640
completely lost it?

45:28.100 --> 45:30.978
I should have checked more carefully.
This is my fault.

45:31.061 --> 45:33.522
How can I not be "brothered" right now?

45:34.815 --> 45:37.985
I'm dying from embarrassment
because of you, seriously!

45:40.404 --> 45:42.948
-Don't "brother" me. Just move.
-Right.

45:43.532 --> 45:44.992
I need some sugar. Damn it.

45:45.075 --> 45:46.869
Goodbye, sir.

45:46.952 --> 45:49.163
Has anyone got a macaron or something?

45:49.747 --> 45:52.583
God, I'm so freaking embarrassed!

46:00.090 --> 46:01.425
So embarrassing.

46:14.438 --> 46:17.775
Sorry to "brother" you,
but may I pass through?

46:17.858 --> 46:19.401
Oh, sure.

46:20.861 --> 46:21.904
Thank you.

46:27.034 --> 46:28.118
Did he say "brother"?

46:50.933 --> 46:52.726
Why did I act like such a child?

47:00.400 --> 47:01.652
Man, I'm beat.

47:14.581 --> 47:15.791
That hits the spot.

47:19.586 --> 47:20.587
Ms. Yun.

47:20.671 --> 47:23.715
From now on, please send the file
before 7 p.m. without exception.

47:23.799 --> 47:25.133
I'm not asking.

47:25.217 --> 47:27.052
I'm going to die of embarrassment.

47:27.135 --> 47:29.054
For the love of…

47:29.555 --> 47:31.557
Why is she lashing out at me so early?

47:31.640 --> 47:32.975
What's the fuss about?

47:38.355 --> 47:41.233
Sorry to brother you,
but I'll be taking this woman.

47:45.696 --> 47:46.864
What's wrong with it?

47:52.744 --> 47:55.622
-Proof that she lives on IG.
-The man to know doesn't know much.

47:55.706 --> 47:57.416
-How are you an author?
-Airhead.

47:57.499 --> 47:59.001
Take some Korean lessons, please.

47:59.084 --> 48:00.794
See? You can be dumb and loaded.

48:00.878 --> 48:02.588
Don't be so harsh. She can't help it.

48:02.671 --> 48:05.173
Who do you think you all are, King Sejong?

48:07.342 --> 48:10.178
If you don't want to read it,
just don't read it!

48:12.055 --> 48:13.640
Seriously!

48:17.269 --> 48:18.228
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

48:18.312 --> 48:19.187
What's this?

48:40.375 --> 48:41.460
Look who it is.

48:41.960 --> 48:43.545
What are you up to? Where are you?

48:43.629 --> 48:45.005
I'm hanging out with Da-yeong.

48:45.088 --> 48:48.759
What? You two met up?
Without telling me about it?

48:49.426 --> 48:52.220
You kept ignoring our messages.
We figured you were busy.

48:53.013 --> 48:55.098
You must be free now,
calling me like this.

48:55.933 --> 48:56.850
Are you mad?

48:57.601 --> 48:58.977
No, I mean…

48:59.728 --> 49:02.064
Don't be. I'm going through a lot.

49:02.814 --> 49:04.733
Where are you? Can I join you guys?

49:06.068 --> 49:08.612
-My boyfriend and Jun-ho will be here.
-Tell her to come.

49:08.695 --> 49:10.447
Want to come? You're welcome to join.

49:10.530 --> 49:13.075
So it's a double date.

49:13.992 --> 49:15.410
Nah, I'll pass.

49:15.494 --> 49:16.954
Okay. Stay in touch.

49:17.037 --> 49:18.330
Yeah.

49:27.589 --> 49:29.132
I want to get away.

50:04.376 --> 50:08.588
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, would you like to go
and meet your new date?

50:08.672 --> 50:11.425
I said I'll pass today.
My subscription's nearly over anyway.

50:14.469 --> 50:15.470
What the…

50:18.265 --> 50:19.391
What is this?

50:24.730 --> 50:27.899
This is driving me crazy.
I said I'll pass.

51:03.769 --> 51:04.853
An office worker?

51:10.984 --> 51:12.444
Nice weather.

52:03.578 --> 52:04.412
Seo Mi-rae.

52:29.521 --> 52:30.355
Is it you?

52:32.983 --> 52:34.234
How…

52:35.819 --> 52:37.529
It's been so long.

52:39.114 --> 52:40.532
Has it been ten years?

52:40.615 --> 52:42.450
He's not a college student anymore.

52:44.452 --> 52:46.037
SPRING, AND YOU

52:46.121 --> 52:47.497
"To be continued"?

52:59.384 --> 53:00.886
So what happened?

53:01.803 --> 53:02.637
What?

53:03.680 --> 53:05.599
I was worried when you disappeared.

53:09.394 --> 53:10.228
Well…

53:10.312 --> 53:11.605
Have you been well?

53:13.732 --> 53:17.736
I knew it was just a ploy
to get me to extend my subscription,

53:18.695 --> 53:20.322
but having seen Seo Eun-ho…

53:25.118 --> 53:25.952
I have.

53:27.495 --> 53:28.663
How about you?

53:29.623 --> 53:30.457
Me too.

53:32.417 --> 53:33.960
…I had to fall for it again.

53:34.461 --> 53:37.047
You've changed a lot, Mi-rae.

53:39.299 --> 53:40.175
Have I?

53:41.551 --> 53:42.385
You too.

53:44.804 --> 53:46.640
It's been ten years, after all.

53:50.143 --> 53:51.353
But you are…

53:54.314 --> 53:56.775
still as pretty as ever.

54:23.593 --> 54:24.427
Welcome…

54:25.011 --> 54:27.639
Oh my God, is there a fire somewhere?

54:27.722 --> 54:30.725
Yes. Fortunately,
we managed to put out the worst of it.

54:31.518 --> 54:32.477
That's good to hear.

54:32.560 --> 54:34.729
There's still a fire that won't go out.

54:35.397 --> 54:36.815
What? Where is it?

54:40.944 --> 54:41.987
It's burning

54:42.779 --> 54:44.114
in my heart for you.

54:48.493 --> 54:51.871
Mi-rae, I've spent my whole life
putting out fires.

54:52.372 --> 54:54.249
But this fire burning for you?

54:55.375 --> 54:56.376
I never

54:57.043 --> 54:58.295
want to put it out.

55:06.594 --> 55:08.555
WOULD YOU LIKE TO MEET
YOUR NEXT BOYFRIEND?

55:08.638 --> 55:09.472
YES

57:16.975 --> 57:21.980
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon
